Alternate titles: Shadow Force, Active Steel

When Murphy is given orders to go back to Mexico, he must use a new technology plane to get there. The plane is technically advanced with a new protection luxury called 'Active Stealth'. The action never stops from then on when a drug cartel abducts military pilot Captain Murphy and his superior. 

Starring:  Daniel Baldwin, Hannes Jaenicke, Lisa Vidal, Andrew Stevens, Fred Williamson

Director Fred Olen Ray
